description: Listen to The Investors Podcast - We Study Billionaires on your Echo or other Alexa device. Just say "We Study Billionaires" to launch the skill. From there, you can listen to the latest podcast by saying "Play" or listen to summaries of the latest episodes by saying "Scan Titles." When scanning, just say "Alexa, Play Next" to hear the full episode.
exampleInteractions: Alexa tell We Study Billionaires To Play
Alexa tell We Study Billionaires To Scan Titles
